{"tid":1555814,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 一人一個新活動！","createTime":"2019-09-09T13:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:49:10.000Z","uid":260531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"76c3245c4a07cb52046cae4441e3791b94e50b5e","tid":1555814,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"係呢場運動入面 我地做咗好多唔同既活動<br />\n有啲一開始以為有啲膠有啲未必成功既活動都有佢既效果<br />\n例如十點鳩叫 例如香港之路等等<br />\n去到依家好似係時候又去諗啲新既活動啦！<br />\n<br />\n有鑒於手足發夢既時候有時會體力不足等等既原因<br />\n咁就俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我提議平日可能揀一日去操fit 自己<br />\n可以係練短跑 長跑 擲鐵餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 游水練氣等等等等<br />\n好似人地啲跑步團咁<br />\n<br />\n一係就team sports 訓練下大家之間既默契<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係大家記得如果真係搞得成就唔好隨便發開口夢 <br />\n唔好講夢話啦<br />\n<br />\n為咗香港大家一齊發揮自己小宇宙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 交啲活動出黎！<br />\n<br />\n我個活動都好brief既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輕屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e22e938218a13c202f4d2e5727ebc3223130af","tid":1555814,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n913獅子山之路 914天水圍 915民陣大遊行"},{"pid":"e1caf30ad9f62e263e1a7df623efaaf39050e81d","tid":1555814,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"推唔郁都推兩推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d9b787358d06afb04fbf977be2cb0d32ffcd57","tid":1555814,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:34:58.000Z","msg":"中秋鐳射燈迷會<br />\n<br />\n堅燈迷果隻"},{"pid":"579ba60b8cb393d5322dda1271cae22c5c3b7351","tid":1555814,"uid":260531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81d9b787358d06afb04fbf977be2cb0d32ffcd57","tid":1555814,"uid":228437,"like":0,